.stitches-sprite(@x: 0, @y: 0, @width: 0, @height: 0) {
    background-position: @x @y;
    width: @width;
    height: @height;
}

.sprite {
    background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    display: block;

    &.sprite-add_user {
        .stitches-sprite(-5px, -5px, 26px, 26px);
    }

    &.sprite-all_user {
        .stitches-sprite(-41px, -5px, 26px, 26px);
    }

    &.sprite-candidatos {
